---
---

<section class="services reveal" id="services">
    <div class="services__header">
        <div class="services__header-ref">
            <span class="services__ref-code">SEC.01</span>
            <span class="services__ref-line"></span>
        </div>
        <p class="services__overline">SERVICE MANIFEST</p>
        <h2 class="services__headline">How I Help</h2>
        <p class="services__description">From early-stage product discovery to scaling engineering organisations — I provide hands-on technical leadership tailored to where your business is today and where it needs to go.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="services__flow">
        <div class="services__step stagger stagger-1">
            <div class="services__step-marker">
                <span class="services__step-number">01</span>
                <span class="services__step-line"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="services__step-content">
                <p class="services__step-label">RECOGNIZE</p>
                <h3 class="services__step-title">When I Step In</h3>
                <p class="services__step-intro">I work with companies when product, technology, and execution need stronger direction, better structure, and clearer ownership.</p>
                <div class="services__accordion">
                    <details class="services__accordion-item">
                        <summary class="services__accordion-summary">You need technical leadership before a full-time CTO makes sense</summary>
                        <p class="services__accordion-body">When product development is moving, but technical decisions still depend too heavily on founders, managers, or individual developers. I step in to create direction, establish ownership, and turn technical uncertainty into structured execution.</p>
                    </details>
                    <details class="services__accordion-item">
                        <summary class="services__accordion-summary">Product, engineering, and business priorities are no longer aligned</summary>
                        <p class="services__accordion-body">When teams are working hard, but progress slows down because priorities conflict, decisions drift, and execution creates rework. I help reconnect business goals, technical decisions, and delivery focus so momentum becomes measurable again.</p>
                    </details>
                    <details class="services__accordion-item">
                        <summary class="services__accordion-summary">Your team delivers, but the current setup will not scale</summary>
                        <p class="services__accordion-body">When delivery depends on improvisation, key people carry too much context, and growth starts creating friction instead of leverage. I help build the structures, workflows, and decision paths that allow teams to move faster without creating more chaos.</p>
                    </details>
                    <details class="services__accordion-item">
                        <summary class="services__accordion-summary">You need clarity before committing to the next phase</summary>
                        <p class="services__accordion-body">When the pressure is real, the next step matters, and nobody has yet turned the situation into a workable plan. I help define priorities, surface trade-offs, and create an execution path that is realistic, actionable, and aligned with the business.</p>
                    </details>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="services__step stagger stagger-2">
            <div class="services__step-marker">
                <span class="services__step-number">02</span>
                <span class="services__step-line"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="services__step-content">
                <p class="services__step-label">SOLVE</p>
                <h3 class="services__step-title">What I Deliver</h3>
                <p class="services__step-intro">Structured support across three areas — from strategic clarity to hands-on execution to scalable operations.</p>
                <div class="services__pane">
                    <div class="services__section">
                        <div class="services__section-header">
                            <span class="services__section-number">01</span>
                            <h3 class="services__section-title">Strategy &amp; Advisory</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="services__section-description">For founders and leadership teams who need technical clarity before committing to a direction.</p>
                        <ul class="services__section-bullets">
                            <li>Technical due diligence</li>
                            <li>Architecture assessment</li>
                            <li>Build vs. buy analysis</li>
                            <li>Product roadmap review</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p class="services__section-ideal">Ideal for: Pre-investment, pivot decisions, scaling planning</p>
                    </div>

                    <hr class="services__divider" />

                    <div class="services__section">
                        <div class="services__section-header">
                            <span class="services__section-number">02</span>
                            <h3 class="services__section-title">Product &amp; Engineering</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="services__section-description">For teams that need hands-on product leadership and engineering execution.</p>
                        <ul class="services__section-bullets">
                            <li>Full-stack development</li>
                            <li>Team setup &amp; mentoring</li>
                            <li>Sprint planning &amp; delivery</li>
                            <li>CI/CD &amp; DevOps</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p class="services__section-ideal">Ideal for: MVPs, rebuilds, team augmentation</p>
                    </div>

                    <hr class="services__divider" />

                    <div class="services__section">
                        <div class="services__section-header">
                            <span class="services__section-number">03</span>
                            <h3 class="services__section-title">Operations &amp; Scale</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="services__section-description">For growing companies that need structure, process, and technical operations at scale.</p>
                        <ul class="services__section-bullets">
                            <li>Engineering process design</li>
                            <li>Hiring &amp; onboarding</li>
                            <li>Performance monitoring</li>
                            <li>Incident management</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p class="services__section-ideal">Ideal for: Series A+, scaling teams, post-launch</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="services__step stagger stagger-3">
            <div class="services__step-marker">
                <span class="services__step-number">03</span>
                <span class="services__step-line"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="services__step-content">
                <p class="services__step-label">ENGAGE</p>
                <h3 class="services__step-title">How We Work Together</h3>
                <p class="services__step-intro">Choose the format that fits your situation — from focused advisory to ongoing CTO-level partnership.</p>

                <div class="services__plans">
                    <div class="services__plan">
                        <div class="services__plan-left">
                            <h4 class="services__plan-title">Hourly Based Consulting</h4>
                            <p class="services__plan-desc">Strategy sessions, architecture reviews, team mentoring, and code review oversight.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="services__plan-price-row">
                            <span class="services__plan-price">$130</span>
                            <span class="services__plan-price-unit">/hour</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="services__plan services__plan--highlighted">
                        <div class="services__plan-left">
                            <h4 class="services__plan-title">Fixed Prototype Iterations</h4>
                            <p class="services__plan-desc">Hands-on product development, sprint planning &amp; delivery, async support, and performance tracking.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="services__plan-price-row">
                            <span class="services__plan-price">$4,999</span>
                            <span class="services__plan-price-unit">/iteration</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="services__plan">
                        <div class="services__plan-left">
                            <h4 class="services__plan-title">Monthly CTO Retainer</h4>
                            <p class="services__plan-desc">Dedicated CTO, board &amp; stakeholder reporting, security &amp; compliance oversight, custom integrations.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="services__plan-price-row">
                            <span class="services__plan-price">$2,499</span>
                            <span class="services__plan-price-unit">/month</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="services__cta">
                    <p class="services__cta-text">Not sure which fits? Let's talk.</p>
                    <a class="services__cta-button" href="#contact">Book a Discovery Call</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
    .services {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        padding: 80px 144px 64px;

        &__header {
            max-width: 600px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        &__header-ref {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }

        &__ref-code {
            font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            color: var(--clr-accent);
        }

        &__ref-line {
            flex: 1;
            height: 1px;
            background: var(--clr-border);
            max-width: 120px;
        }

        &__overline {
            font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.18em;
            color: var(--clr-text-muted);
        }

        &__headline {
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 64px;
            color: var(--clr-text-primary);
            letter-spacing: -2px;
            line-height: 0.95;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        &__description {
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: var(--clr-text-muted);
            line-height: 1.65;
            max-width: 520px;
        }

        &__flow {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        &__step {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        &__step-marker {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            width: 40px;
        }

        &__step-number {
            font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--clr-accent);
            line-height: 1;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        &__step-line {
            flex: 1;
            width: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--clr-accent), transparent);
            margin-top: 12px;
            min-height: 40px;
        }

        &__step-label {
            font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            color: var(--clr-accent);
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }

        &__step-content {
            flex: 1;
            padding-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        &__step-title {
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 2.25rem;
            color: var(--clr-text-primary);
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        &__step-intro {
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--clr-text-muted);
            line-height: 1.65;
            max-width: 560px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        &__accordion {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        &__accordion-item {
            border-top: 1px solid var(--clr-border-light);

            &:last-child {
                border-bottom: 1px solid var(--clr-border-light);
            }
        }

        &__accordion-summary {
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--clr-text-primary);
            padding: 1.125rem 0;
            cursor: pointer;
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 1rem;

            &::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }

            &::after {
                content: '+';
                font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
                font-size: 1.25rem;
                font-weight: 700;
                color: var(--clr-accent);
                flex-shrink: 0;
            }
        }

        &__accordion-item[open] > &__accordion-summary::after {
            content: '−';
        }

        &__accordion-body {
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--clr-text-muted);
            line-height: 1.7;
            padding: 0 0 1.125rem;
            max-width: 640px;
        }

        &__pane {
            border-top: 1px solid var(--clr-border-light);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--clr-border-light);
        }

        &__section {
            padding: 32px 0;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            grid-template-rows: auto auto auto;
            column-gap: 2.5rem;
            row-gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        &__section-header {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: baseline;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        &__section-number {
            font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1;
            color: var(--clr-accent);
        }

        &__section-title {
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 28px;
            color: var(--clr-text-primary);
            line-height: 1.1;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        &__section-description {
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--clr-text-muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
            grid-column: 1;
        }

        &__section-bullets {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.35rem;
            grid-column: 2;
            grid-row: 2 / 4;
            align-self: center;

            li {
                font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
                font-size: 13px;
                color: var(--clr-text-muted);
                padding-left: 1.25rem;
                position: relative;

                &::before {
                    content: '>';
                    position: absolute;
                    left: 0;
                    color: var(--clr-accent);
                    font-size: 11px;
                }
            }
        }

        &__section-ideal {
            font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: var(--clr-text-muted);
            grid-column: 1;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        }

        &__divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--clr-border-light);
            margin: 0;
        }

        &__plans {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            width: 100%;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--clr-border-light);
        }

        &__plan {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 2rem;
            padding: 24px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--clr-border-light);

            &--highlighted {
                border-left: 2px solid var(--clr-accent);
                padding-left: 24px;
                margin-left: -26px;
                background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 229, 160, 0.03), transparent 60%);
            }
        }

        &__plan-left {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 4px;
            flex: 1;
        }

        &__plan-title {
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 22px;
            color: var(--clr-text-primary);
            line-height: 1.1;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        &__plan-desc {
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--clr-text-muted);
            line-height: 1.55;
        }

        &__plan-price-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: baseline;
            gap: 2px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        &__plan-price {
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 36px;
            color: var(--clr-text-primary);
            line-height: 1;
        }

        &__plan-price-unit {
            font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--clr-text-muted);
        }

        &__cta {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-top: 24px;
        }

        &__cta-text {
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--clr-text-muted);
        }

        &__cta-button {
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            line-height: 1;
            color: var(--clr-bg-primary);
            background: var(--clr-accent);
            border-radius: 2px;
            padding: 14px 36px;
            transition: opacity 0.2s ease;

            &:hover {
                opacity: 0.85;
            }
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 1440px) {
        .services { padding: 80px 80px 64px; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .services {
            padding: 64px 2rem 48px;

            &__header { max-width: 100%; }
            &__headline { font-size: 48px; }

            &__section {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                padding: 24px 0;
            }

            &__section-bullets {
                grid-column: 1;
                grid-row: auto;
            }

            &__plan {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 1rem;

                &--highlighted {
                    margin-left: -2rem;
                    padding-left: calc(24px + (2rem - 26px));
                }
            }
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 375px) {
        .services { padding: 64px 1.25rem 48px; }
    }
</style>
